summary: An Ordinance providing for the improvement of the alley in Block Seventy-two (72) of Terry's First Addition to the City of Seattle, same being the alley between Eighth Avenue and Ninth Avenue, from Madison Street to Marion Street, by grading and bulkheading the same in accordance with Majority Petition, being File No. 30655, and providing for the payment therefor by the mode of "Immediate Payment," under provisions of Ordinance No. 5693 of said city, approved December 6, 1899.
